-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT avg(s.totalamount::numeric ) as average_order
from warehouse.fact_sales s

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT g.countryname, sum(s.totalamount)::numeric as totalamount

from warehouse.fact_sales s 
join warehouse.dim_geography g on s.geographykey  = g.geographykey 

group by g.countryname

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT d.first_day_of_month , sum(s.totalamount)::numeric as totalamount  
from warehouse.fact_sales s
join warehouse.dim_date d on s.boughtdatekey  = d.datekey 

group by d.first_day_of_month

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT  g.cityname  , d.day_of_week   , sum(s.nbrboughtpostcards::numeric) as total_qty
from warehouse.fact_sales s
join warehouse.dim_geography g on g.geographykey  = s.geographykey 
join warehouse.dim_date d on d.datekey = s.boughtdatekey 

group by g.cityname  , d.day_of_week

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT  c.channelname , d.first_day_of_month::timestamp, sum(s.totalamount::numeric ) as total_sales
from warehouse.fact_sales s
join warehouse.dim_channel c on s.channelkey   = c.channelkey  
join warehouse.dim_date d on d.datekey= s.boughtdatekey
group by c.channelname , d.first_day_of_month::timestamp
